Motormaster hears Scourge, "Astroblast, stay in flight, we may need to
depart quickly" he walks over to the hatch, and opens it, hoping out, and
waiting for Stratus to follow. "Greetings Scourge. I'm not quite sure
myself, but this is where the signal came from." He looks around, (This is
where you come in Kevin)
